title: Measure for Measure, or Beauty the Best Advocate

items: THe Duke of Savoy — — — Mr. Arnold.
Angelo his Deputy Privately Marry'd to Mariana. Mr. Betterton.
Escalus. Chief Minister under Angelo — — Mr. Berry.
Claudio, A Young Nobleman, of an Ancient Family, but Decay'd Fortune ; one that Behav'd himself well in the War, privately Marry'd to Julietta. Mr. Verbrugen.
Isabella, Sister to Claudio, a Young Votary, de sign'd, for want of Fortune, to a Nunnery. Mrs. Bracegirdle.
Julietta, A Lady of Considerable Fortune ; but left in the hands of a Covetous Uncle, who is a Hypocrite, and will give Consent to none, that he may not part with it, Mrs. Bowman.
Mariana A Lady of no Fortune, secretly Marry'd to Angelo, Mrs. Prince.
